# ==============================================
# SWITCHING GUIDE
# ==============================================
#
# To use LOCAL database:
#   1. Set: DB_PROVIDER=local
#   2. Ensure PostgreSQL is running locally
#   3. Run: npm run db:push
#
# To use SUPABASE:
#   1. Set: DB_PROVIDER=supabase
#   2. Ensure Supabase project is active
#   3. Run: npm run db:push
#
# After switching, restart dev server:
#   npm run dev
